    "shortName": {
      "zh": "B-12",
      "en": "B-12"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "跳蚤市场: 8,888₽ | 物品价值: 3,453 | Jaeger报价: 2,072₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 4,489₽\n购买渠道 @ Skier 等级2 < 3,971₽\n\nB-12导气管上悬浮式导轨需安装在B-11护木的侧导轨上，通过在武器导气管上方和护木侧面构成导轨的形式，可实现复杂瞄具与战术配件的相互结合。",
      "en": "跳蚤市场: 8,888₽ | 物品价值: 3,453 | Jaeger报价: 2,072₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 4,489₽\n购买渠道 @ Skier 等级2 < 3,971₽\n\nThe B-12 gas tube overhanging rail mount is installed on the side rail of the B-11 or B-10 handguards and provides a weapon with means of installing a complex of sights and tactical devices by forming rail mounts over the weapon's gas tube and on the side of the handguard. Manufactured by Zenit."
    },
